column2: SELECT to upload -- the results to the SAS (Science Archive Server) for FITS file retrieval. SELECT ALL    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,    p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMag_g,    s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE     p.cModelMag_r < #    AND s.class = &&&
